==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Casque
<hw>Casque</hw> <pr>(k⟦adot⟧sk)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>casque</ets>, fr. Sp. <ets>casco</ets> See <er>Cask</er>.]</ety>
<def>A piece of defensive or ornamental armor (with or without a vizor)
for the head and neck; a helmet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His <qex>casque</qex> overshadowed with brilliant plumes.</q>
<rj><qau>Prescott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cass</ent>⟦br⟧
